      <description>DAMASCUS – The Syrian flag isn’t just waving over the neighborhoods of Damascus: now it’s also painted on their storefronts. In the Syrian capital, shopkeepers say that government officials are compelling them to paint the Syrian flag on all shop doors in the city of Damascus.</description>
